data.description: 3% Assumable Loan!! Priced to Move! Quality Custom all brick in a parklike setting! Elegant features like arched doorways, crown moulding, 20x20 tiles, hard wood in the dining room, 10 ft smooth ceilings, recessed lighting greet you as you enter. Spacious Great room perfect for your family & entertaining! Open  kitchen where the chef will enjoy stainless appliances, granite countertops, breakfast bar & nook. The master suite is large & private. The master bathroom has a large garden tub, separate tile shower & a huge walk in closet. Gulf Power Earth Cents home features R-13 wall & R-38 ceiling insulation. Solar Panels provide all of the power you need. Only a nominal $25/mo power bill!!!
